Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.23,0:00:06.93,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不做厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.93,0:00:09.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,如果在食戟上输给你的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.08,0:00:12.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我就再也不身负「幸平」的招牌
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:16.02,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,发誓不再出现在专业的厨房中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.86,0:00:19.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话与一百把厨具的价值相称了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:23.13,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便节省你一个工序吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:26.53,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,第二轮比赛的题目是西餐的主食
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.15,0:00:28.39,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我会做这个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:30.24,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,牛肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.39,0:00:31.32,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:32.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,你在透露些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.80,0:00:34.84,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要把你要做的料理暴露出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:36.65,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,反正都会被预测出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.78,0:00:38.57,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,输了的话再也不能当厨师了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.85,0:00:40.78,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,幸平 我看错你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.88,0:00:44.59,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,对于你来说料理是那种随手可弃的东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.94,0:00:45.68,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,水户同学
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.70,0:00:46.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.22,0:00:48.03,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,肉魅亲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.70,0:00:49.48,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,创真君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.44,0:00:52.00,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,不当厨师了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,把塔克米君的半月刀夺回来就足够…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.55,0:00:55.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs52.5\pos(936,1005)}mezza luna
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.46,0:00:56.50,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,那样还不够
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.79,0:01:00.28,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,我要你把到现在抢过来的一百把厨具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.42,0:01:02.46,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,物归原主
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.82,0:01:05.35,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,赌上我作为厨师的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.59,0:01:06.77,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,也会将你打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.19,0:01:08.55,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,美作昴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.08,0:01:11.04,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,成立了 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.82,0:01:12.89,shiki zw,NTP,0,0,0,,食戟
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.02,0:01:13.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,——————OP——————
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:37.54,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}思い描いてるイメージより遙か向こう側へ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.03,0:01:37.54,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}比心中描绘的意象更遥远的彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:43.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}創り上げて行く　真実はまだ遠く
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.13,0:01:43.97,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}在一笔笔叙写  那真实还在远方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}果てない旅路
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.84,0:01:47.85,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}如无尽的旅途
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.89,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}お互いのプライドを研ぎ澄ませよぜ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.89,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}来将各自的自尊心研磨透亮
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:57.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}言葉なんて飾りは開けさせりやいい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.23,0:01:57.90,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}敞开任何言语之类的装饰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:07.32,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}ぶつかり合い　磨かれていく　rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.02,0:02:07.32,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相互碰撞 相互摩擦 rolling stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.99,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}出會いは　shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.45,0:02:09.99,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}相遇是 shockwave shockwave
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:15.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}まだ知らない世界へ歩き始めた
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.03,0:02:15.08,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}向未知的世界迈出脚步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}無謀な挑戦者さ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.08,0:02:17.63,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}无谋的挑战者
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:22.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}手にした刃で明日を切り開けばいいんだろ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.63,0:02:22.96,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}只要用手中的刀劈开明天就可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.05,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}誰かのもんじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.01,0:02:25.05,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}这并不是別人的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}自分だけのストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.17,0:02:28.84,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}是只属于自己的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:34.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an7}cause we are still rough diamonds on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.97,0:02:34.81,OPED,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\an3}因为我们都是未经琢磨的钻石！
